{"tid":1046701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又傳]  英國傳或限制電訊商用華為設備","createTime":"2019-03-04T12:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T03:24:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3981007fd90894b5c9acf9464ba4a09078d984c5","tid":1046701,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"英國傳或限制電訊商用華為設備<br />\n<br />\n英國據報可能限制電訊商使用中國電訊巨擘華為的通訊設備。<br />\n<br />\n英國監管部門計劃於未來數周內，公布電訊業基建的檢討報告。英國《金融時報》引述消息指，雖然當局無意全面排除華為，但建議限制流動電訊商使用華為設備的比例，不能超過整個網絡的一半。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，此次報告旨在回應社會對華為技術日益增長的安全問題。當局相信，上述建議有助當地5G網絡順利發展，同時不過分依賴中國供應設備。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府發言人未有正面回應報道，僅稱最重要是網絡可靠和安全，正檢視通訊基建供應鏈，適時公布最終結論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2071735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2071735&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4FGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=b6eb97fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2071735</a>"},{"pid":"315a234798353089d305f3d634ba479576064548","tid":1046701,"uid":60338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"仆街。撚夠未呀。呢幾個月D新聞撚黎撚去"},{"pid":"863a964c8bd414b92fbb4787379ca9708ae873aa","tid":1046701,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"315a234798353089d305f3d634ba479576064548","tid":1046701,"uid":60338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"仆街。撚夠未呀。呢幾個月D新聞撚黎撚去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"FT同WSJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英美兩大鳩傳報紙<br />\n隔兩三日又有消息人士出嚟講嘢打倒自己幾日前嘅新聞"},{"pid":"d10a8ea0795dbc36b6f0e1923b10725b4d9c3c08","tid":1046701,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aTRZB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.